y widget below to see how it works.' },
  { slideIndex: 2, src: `${base}/audio/modules/m6-knowledge-check.mp3`, transcript: 'Time to test what you have learned. Five questions on the Scorecard framework. You need eighty percent to mark this module complete. Take your time.' },
